headline: Is Extra Space Storage Worth a Closer Look After Its 7.5% Monthly Rally?
summary: Thinking about what to do with your Extra Space Storage shares, or eyeing a new entry point? You are not alone. The stock has been anything but boring in the past months. Over the last week, shares have dipped by 0.8%, offering a minor breather after a strong 7.5% climb over the last month. If you zoom out to this year, the picture is a bit more modest, with a 1.7% gain so far. A look back at the last five years reminds us what patience can achieve, with a hefty 56.3% gain for long-term...
